description:

name: War & Peace Tee
description: The balance between war and peace can be as fragile as a word. This shirt was designed to depict that very fine line on which we all walk. Doves, often the symbol of peace, fly in a flock on one side while the other is blazoned with an unloading gun. the only thing separating these two is a simple word, laced with blood. Armistice Ar·mi·stice [ahr-muh-stis] – (noun) a temporary suspension of hostilities by agreement of the warring parties.
